text=(:Summary: 如何创建像一些有序、无序列表，引用块，代码块:) %0a(:title 文本格式规则:)%0a>>rframe font-size:smaller%3c%3c%0a!! 目录%0a* [[#Paragraphs|段落]]%0a* [[#IndentedParagraphs|缩进段落，''引用''(Quotes)]]%0a* [[#BulletedLists|无需列表、有序列表]]%0a* [[#DefinitionLists|定义列表]]%0a* [[#WhitespaceRules|空白规则]] %0a* [[#HorizontalLine|水平线]]%0a* [[#Emphasis|强调]]%0a* [[#References|资源链接]]%0a* [[#Headings|标题]]%0a* [[#EscapeSequence|Code代码]]%0a* [[PmWiki/Special Characters| 特殊字符]]%0a* [[#Tables |表格]]%0a>>%3c%3c%0a这个页面提供了更多有效的PmWiki支持的Markup标记列表。  %0a如果你需要使用，请往下看。%0a%0a要练习一下这些语法规则，请到[[Main/Wiki Sandbox|沙盒]]中练习，而非在本页。%0a----%0a%0a!! [[#Paragraphs]] 段落%0a%0a另起一段，只需要按回车空一行就可以了。%0a%0aWords on two lines in a row will '''wrap and fill''' as needed (the normal XHTML behavior).  To turn off the automatic filling, use the [@(:linebreaks:)@] directive above the paragraph.%0a%0a* 在一行结尾插入[@\@] (一个反斜杠) 可以将当前行加入到下一节。%0a* 在一行结尾插入[@\\@] (两个反斜杠)强制换一行。%0a* 在一行结尾插入[@\\\@] (三个反斜杠)强制换两行。%0a* 使用[@[[%3c%3c]]@]插入一个可以清空浮动元素的换行。%0a%0a%0a!! [[#IndentedParagraphs]] 缩进段落 ''(Quotes)''（引用）%0a%0a使用([@->@])在段落开头可以产生一个整段缩进。像这样([@--->@])，更多的破折号产生更大的缩进。%0a%0a(:markup:)%0a->从其有座山，山里有座庙，庙里有个老和尚和小和尚。老和尚在对小和尚讲故事：“从其有座山，山里有座庙，庙里有个老和尚和小和尚。老和尚在对小和尚讲故事……”%0a(:markupend:)%0a%0a使用([@-%3c@])可以减小段落缩进，更上面一个刚好相反，越多的破折号(像这样[@---%3c@]) 缩进也越小。示例：%0a%0a(:markup:)%0a-%3cFour score and seven years ago our fathers placed upon this continent a new nation, conceived in liberty and dedicated to the proposition that all men are created equal. %0a(:markupend:)%0a%0a(:markup:)%0a--%3cFour score and seven years ago our fathers placed upon this continent a new nation, conceived in liberty and dedicated to the proposition that all men are created equal.  And that food would be good too.%0a(:markupend:)%0a%0aBlocks of text to which [@(:linebreaks:)@] has been applied can be indented by preceding the first line of the block with indention arrows ([@->@]) and aligning subsequent lines under the first. An unindented line stops the block indentation.  See [[Cookbook:Markup Tricks]] for an example.%0a%0a%0a!! [[#BulletedLists]] 无序列表和有序列表%0a%0a无序列表使用星号（*），有序列表使用井号（#）:%0a%0a(:markup:) %0a* First-level list item%0a** Second-level list item%0a### Order this%0a#### And this (optional)%0a### Then this%0a** Another second-level item%0a* A first-level item: cooking%0a## Prepare the experiment%0a### Unwrap the pop-tart%0a### Insert the pop-tart into the toaster%0a## Begin cooking the pop tart%0a## Stand back%0a(:markupend:)%0a%0a(:markup:)%0a# A list is terminated%0aby the first line that is not a list.%0a# Also terminate a list using the escape sequence [@[==]@]%0a[==]%0a# Continue a list item by lining%0a  up the text with leading whitespace.%0a# Use a forced linebreak \\%0a  to force a newline in your list item.%0a(:markupend:)%0a%0a(:markup:)%0a## Text between list items can cause numbering to restart%0a## %25item value=3%25 this can be dealt with%0a(:markupend:)%0a%0a更多内容详见：[[PmWiki:ListStyles]]和[[Cookbook:WikiStylesPlus]]。%0a%0a%0a!! [[#DefinitionLists]] 定义列表%0a>>rframe%3c%3c%0a'''这是一个很有用的%25red%25*%25%25 新功能'''\\%0aWhen you define terms using this markup\\%0aPmWiki will recognize them as [[PageTextVariables]]\\%0athat you can use on any page or [[PageList(s)]].\\%0a[-%25red%25* Added%25%25 in PmWiki version %25red%252.2.0%25%25-]%0a>>%3c%3c%0aDefinition lists are made by placing colons at the left margin (and between each term and definition):%0a%0a(:markup:)%0a:项目:项目定义%0a(:markupend:)%0a%0a[[#WhitespaceRules]]%0a!!  空白规则%0a%0aWhitespace indentation in lists.  Any line that begins with whitespace ''and aligns'' with a previous list item (whether bulleted, numbers or definitional) is considered to be "within" that list item.  Text folds and wraps as normal, and the [@(:linebreaks:)@] directive is honored. %0a%0a(:markup:) %0a# First-level item\\%0a  Whitespace used to continue item on a new line%0a# Another first-level item%0a  # Whitespace combined with a single # to create a new item one level deeper%0a(:markupend:)%0a%0aOtherwise, lines that begin with whitespace are treated as ''preformatted text'', using a monospace font and not generating linebreaks except where explicitly indicated in the markup.  Note to administrators: Starting with version 2.2.0-beta41, this feature can be modified using $EnableWSPre.  (Another way to create preformatted text blocks is by using the [=[@...@]=] markup.)%0a%0a!! [[#HorizontalLine]] 水平分隔线%0a%0a使用4个或以上的破折号([=----=])可以在当前行插入水平分割线。%0a%0a[[#Emphasis]]%0a!!  强调和字符格式%0a%0a* Enclose text in doubled single-quotes ([=''text''=]), i.e., ''two apostrophes'', for emphasis (usually ''italics'')%0a* Enclose text in tripled single-quotes ([='''text'''=]), i.e. ''three apostrophes'', for strong (usually '''bold''')%0a* Enclose text in five single-quotes ([='''''text'''''=]), or triples within doubles (''five apostrophes''), for strong emphasis (usually '''''bold italics''''')%0a* Enclose text in doubled at-signs ([=@@text@@=]) for @@monospace@@ text%0a* Use [=[+large+]=] for [+large+] text, [=[++larger++]=] for [++larger++], [=[-small-]=] for [-small-] text, and [=[--smaller--]=] for [--smaller--].%0a* Emphasis can be used multiple times within a line, but cannot span across markup line boundaries (i.e., you can't put a paragraph break in the middle of bold text).%0a* [='~italic~'=] and [='*bold*'=]  are available if enabled in config.php%0a%0a其它样式 %0a(:markup:)%0a'+大字体+', '-小字体-', '^上标^', '_下标_', %0a%0a{+插入文字（增加下划线）+}, %0a%0a{-删除文字（增加删除线）-}%0a(:markupend:)%0a* [@`WikiWord@] `WikiWord neutralisation%0a%0a更多关于高级文本样式的设置，请参考[[Wiki Styles|Wiki样式]]。%0a%0a[[#References]]%0a!!  资源链接%0a%0a* 在页面名前后像这样 [=[[text formatting rules]]=] 增加两个方括号可以创建一个链接。%0a* On some PmWiki installations, capitalized words joined together (e.g., [[WikiWord]]s) can also be used to make references to other pages without needing the double-brackets.%0a* 以"@@http:@@", "@@ftp:@@", "@@gopher:@@", "@@mailto:@@",或"@@news:@@" 开头的[=URLs=]地址会像 http://www.pmichaud.com/toast 这样自动显示为链接。%0a* [=URLs=]地址中以@@.gif@@, @@.jpg@@或@@.png@@ 结尾的图片链接会直接显示图片。%0a* Links with arbitrary text can be created as either [=[[=]''target'' | ''text'']] or [=[[=]''text'' -> ''target''[=]]=].  ''Text'' can be an image URL, in which case the image becomes the link to the remote ''url'' or ''[[WikiWord]]''.%0a* [[#Anchors]] 给页面增加锚点请使用@@[=[[#target]]=]@@。%0a更多[[Links|链接]]内容。%0a%0a[[#Headings]]%0a!!标题%0a%0a插入标题，在标题前使用感叹号('''!''') 。详细如下：%0a%0a(:markup:)%0a!! 标题2%0a!!! 标题3%0a!!!! 标题4%0a!!!!! 标题5%0a(:markupend:)%0a%0a值得注意的是，一级标题已经被用在了PmWiki的页面标题中，所以编辑的页面内容需要从H2开始。这样可能利于搜索（引擎）。%0a%0a详见：[[Cookbook:Numbered Headers]] 。%0a%0a[[#EscapeSequence]]%0a!!Code代码%0a%0a任何在[=[= 和=]=]中的内容都会被直接显示，但是段落是被重新格式化的。%0a%0a%0a要插入一段格式化过的文本内容，请在内容前后使用[=[@...@]=] 标记。它既不处理文本（通常是一段代码）中的内容，也不会重新格式化它。示例：%0a%0a(:markup:)%0a[@%0a这是一段[[PmWiki.PmWiki]]代码 %0a'$CurrentTime $[by] $AuthorLink:  [=$ChangeSummary=]'; #前面是代码，我是人见人爱的注释%0a@]%0a(:markupend:)%0a%0aThe multiline @@[=[@...@]=]@@ is a block markup, and in order to change the styling of these preformatted text blocks, you need to apply a "block" WikiStyle.%0a%0a(:markup:)[=%25block blue%25[@ %0a  The font color of %0a  this text is blue%0a@]=]%0a%0aIt is also useful to use [@[= =]@] within other wiki structures, as this enables the inclusion of new lines in text values.  The example below shows how to include a multi-line value in a hidden form field.%0a%0a->[@(:input hidden message "[=Line1%0aLine2=]":)@]%0a%0a!! 注释%0a使用[@ (:一些注释内容:) @] 添加注释。%0a%0a[[#SpecialCharacters]]%0a!!  特殊字符%0a(:include SpecialCharacters:)%0a%0a[[#Tables]]%0a!!  表格%0a%0a[[Tables|表格]]中，一个单元格前后用两个竖线（'||'）包裹起来。%0aA cell with leading and trailing spaces is centered; a cell with leading spaces is right-aligned; all other cells are left-aligned.  An empty cell will cause the previous cell to span multiple columns.  (There is currently no mechanism for spanning multiple rows.)  A line beginning with '||' specifies the table attributes for subsequent tables. A '!' as the first character in a cell provides emphasis that can be used to provide headings.%0a%0a(:markup:)%0a||border=1 width=50%25%0a||!表格||!标题||!示例||%0a||!左边   || 中             || 右边||%0a||石头    ||!  大剪刀       ||   布||%0a||        || 中间是一位天使 ||     ||%0a||        || 合并一列       ||||%0a(:markupend:)%0a%0a更多内容详见：[[Table Directives|表格高级指令]]。%0a%0a!!!更多内容%0a请看[[Markup Master Index|这里]]。
